Halo, Tuan Deshmukh.
Halo, Ibu.  Silakan datang.

00:05:18.403 --> 00:05:21.319
Temui Tuan Deshmukh
dan Nyonya Deshmukh.

00:05:22.653 --> 00:05:23.570
Sai..

00:05:23.695 --> 00:05:26.818
Tuan Deshmukh adalah
salah satu sahabat ayahmu.

00:05:27.236 --> 00:05:28.986
Halo Pak.  Halo, Ibu.

